{"word":"G2546 - κἀκεῖ - kakeî - kak-i' - And there","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κἀκεῖ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kakeî</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kak-i'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">And there</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அங்கே, இடத்தில், அவ்விடம் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. and there"},{"paragraph":"2. there also"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2532 - καί - kaí - kahee/2532\">G2532</a> and <a href=\"#/G1563 - ἐκεῖ - ekeî - ek-i'/1563\">G1563</a>; <i>likewise in that place:</i> - and there, there (thither) also.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}